  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose is the evaluation of life quality of Fibromyalgia patients. The
      investigators' main hypothesis includes the role of geographical, sociological, psychological
      and physical activity on life quality.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
